citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:00 pm on August
10, 2022. I spoke with the licensee on the phone and was informed that they have moved the dog kennel to a new site in
a different town. I instructed licensee to contact the office with their new address so that a new site inspection can be
completed.
End Section

Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries. 
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:00 pm on August 
10, 2022.  I spoke with the licensee on the phone and was informed that they have moved the dog kennel to a new site in 
a different town.  I instructed licensee to contact the office with their new  address so that a new site inspection can be 
completed. 
 
 
 
End Section
